      "link": "https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:activity:7032007586929344513?commentUrn=urn%3Ali%3Acomment%3A%28activity%3A7032007586929344513%2C7032413508872941568%29&dashCommentUrn=urn%3Ali%3Afsd_comment%3A%287032413508872941568%2Curn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A7032007586929344513%29",
      "text": "Thank you Honza and everyone else who helped.\n\nOur community is expanding, and we make use of little we have to grow the community. The chilly conditions in Prague will always be in my memory. I have never experienced such weather in my life. It's hot in Namibia. \n\nTo us, every donation is greatly appreciated. The conference's leftover funds are invested in other local Python activities, buying books, and students with computers and etc .\n\nPeople in Czech are friendly and i love it.",
